  m_Name: Study
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CodexEntry
  title: Study
  description: 'The study in a wealthy household was used for reading, writing, managing
    correspondence, and conducting private family matters. In some homes, especially
    those with children, the study also doubled as a space for learning and quiet
    play. It often contained desks, cabinets, and personal objects that reflected
    both education and family life. '
